        "gg720e49VOk_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_x4i5pmx4i5pmx4i5_1.png",
        "gg720e49VOk_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Homework-A-Help-or-a-Hindrance-900x675.jpg",
        "gg8U7KKNzEG_text": "<strong>My Recommendation</strong>",
        "ggC1d7H_Cy0_text": "<p>Most men on Flomax don't have the full picture.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>You'll need it forever.</strong> Your prostate never shrinks. The inflammation never cools.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Many men deal with dizziness every time they stand up.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Others experience<strong> retrograde ejaculation.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Low blood pressure that gets dangerous during physical activity.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And for many men, <strong>it keeps working less and less over time as tolerance builds.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>One of my patients told me:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>\"My doctor kept increasing my dose. Then even the highest dose stopped helping. He said surgery might be next. That's when I started looking for something else.\"</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Meanwhile, the inflammation is still burning.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The prostate is still growing.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>The drug is just papering over it.</strong></p>",
        "ggDz1sAdji7_text": "<p>If you are waking up multiple times a night, dealing with weak flow, or never feeling like you fully empty...</p><p><br>Click below and try MeridEase Labs' Pumpkin Seed Oil and Saw Palmetto Softgels.</p><p><br>Based on my research and what I have seen with my own patients, there is a strong chance it outperforms what you are currently using for long-term results.</p><p><br>60-day guarantee. Zero risk.</p>",
        "ggFHX5C0Gbe_text": "<strong>The Question Every Man Is Asking</strong>",
        "ggG-7I2VKMm_text": "<p>I wasn't going to trust supplement marketing. <strong>I needed real data.</strong><br><br>Here's what I did:</p><ul><li>Reviewed 9 peer-reviewed studies on pumpkin seed oil and prostate inflammation.</li><li>Interviewed 47 men who had been using the softgels for at least 30 days.</li><li>Monitored 14 of my own patients who added the softgels to their routine.</li><li>Tried the softgels myself.</li></ul>",
        "ggGMAIS7s5m_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_4ty0o4ty0o4ty0o4_1.png",
        "ggGMAIS7s5m_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_4ty0o4ty0o4ty0o4_1.png",
        "ggIIxvV39Tx_text": "<p>And the saw palmetto extract adds one more layer.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Its fatty acids <strong>block DHT from binding to prostate cell receptors.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>So DHT is double-blocked.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Production goes down. Receptor binding goes down.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And saw palmetto independently calms the bladder neck, reducing the muscle spasm that triggers urgency <strong>before your bladder is even close to full.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>That's why this works when generic saw palmetto capsules don't.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Two ingredients. Three fires out.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Not masked. Not pushed down temporarily. Extinguished.</p>",
        "ggKKnEsidaS_text": "<p><i>Clever marketing or a real answer for men who can't sleep through the night? I looked at the actual science.</i></p>",
        "ggLMkTR0k_S_alt": "Alt Image",
        "ggLMkTR0k_S_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/main_71bc4de8-6061-46ae-8a7a-0c4ffe27958c.jpg",
        "ggLMkTR0k_S_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_4s4q4t4s4q4t4s4q_1.png",
        "ggLMkTR0k_S_title": "Image Title",
        "ggMnidJ-jPR_text": "<strong>Why Your Doctor Has Never Mentioned This</strong>",
        "ggNaDtqUOVv_text": "<strong>My Professional Assessment</strong>",
        "ggPWMLeDUZm_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_gwo43kgwo43kgwo4.jpg",
        "ggUfcz6uXll_text": "<p>Here's what shocked me.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>For most of my career, I was trained that <strong>BPH is a hormone problem.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Too much DHT. The prostate grows. Block the hormone or relax the muscles. That's the standard plan.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But that's only half the story.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>The research shows BPH starts with inflammation.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Chronic, low-grade inflammation inside the prostate tissue.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Inflammatory signals called IL-6 and TNF-alpha flood the area.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Immune cells rush in.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The tissue swells and turns rigid.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>And rigid tissue does not relax between bathroom trips.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>That's why you feel the urge even right after you went.</p><p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p>That's why you never fully empty.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Then DHT shows up and <strong>binds far more easily to inflamed tissue than healthy tissue.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>So now you have two things feeding each other.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Inflammation making the tissue rigid. DHT making the prostate grow faster.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>That's why men who try a generic saw palmetto capsule feel nothing.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Saw palmetto alone only touches DHT.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The inflammation keeps burning.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But there's a critical difference.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Flomax relaxes the muscles around your urethra for a few hours. You take it, it helps, then it wears off. Your prostate never shrinks. The inflammation never stops. You're fully dependent on it just to get through the night.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>MeridEase Labs' cold-pressed pumpkin seed oil does something different.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It delivers a full complex of phytosterols directly to the inflamed prostate tissue.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>They block the cytokine signals. They calm the immune cell rush. The tissue starts to soften.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>When the tissue softens, the urethra stops being squeezed so tight.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Flow improves. The urge settles. Nighttime trips drop.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>MeridEase Labs isn't masking the problem.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>It's putting out the fire.</strong></p>",
        "ggVFnBpU7Xx_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong>First-time customers only!</strong></span></p>",
        "ggWjkwDyXuj_text": "<strong>⚠️ Only 220 Packs at 55% Off — Price increases when sold out</strong>",
        "ggXJohDDRgt_text": "<strong>What I Found: The Science</strong>",
        "ggaBF89G2wF_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/766x415_Flomax_Side_Effects.jpg",
