        "ggaG0C73vSq_text": "<p>Here's the uncomfortable truth I have to share as a physician.<br><br><strong>MeridEase Labs' softgels are not a prescription drug.</strong><br><br>That means:</p><ul><li>No pharmaceutical company profits from them.</li><li>No drug reps educating doctors about them.</li><li>No insurance billing code for recommending them.</li><li>No incentive for a doctor to bring it up.</li></ul><p><br>I asked 13 urologists in my network about it.<br><br>Only one had ever heard of using pumpkin seed oil for BPH.<br><br>None had recommended it to a patient.<br><br><strong>Not because it doesn't work. Because they didn't know it existed.</strong><br><br>The medical system is built around prescriptions. Everything else is invisible.</p>",
        "ggblP80kboX_text": "<strong>Who Should Try This?</strong>",
        "ggdAN9Q1Dgi_text": "<p>After 90 days of reviewing the science and watching my own patients...</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Yes. MeridEase Labs' Pumpkin Seed Oil and Saw Palmetto Softgels work. And for most men over 50, they go after something Flomax never touches.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Not faster than Flomax at first. Flomax wins on speed.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But <strong>cooling actual inflammation versus relaxing muscles temporarily?</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>MeridEase wins decisively.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>No dependency.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>No retrograde ejaculation.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>No blood pressure crashes.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>No building tolerance month after month.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Actual reduction in prostate swelling over time.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>That is the difference between masking a problem and solving it.</p>",
        "ggdhjRMas5d_text": "Order Now<br>And Save Up To&nbsp;<br>55%",
        "ggeI6Clv8WX_text": "If you've tried Flomax, finasteride, or prostate supplements without sleeping through the night...<br><br>...chances are your prostate is still inflamed.<br><br>That's the real problem most doctors miss.<br><br>What if you could stop waking up 4, 5, 6 times a night...<br><br>...not by relaxing muscles for a few hours...<br><br>...but by cooling the inflammation that's keeping your prostate swollen in the first place?<br><br>That's exactly what MeridEase Labs' Pumpkin Seed Oil and Saw Palmetto Softgels are built to do.<br><br>A natural way to target the root cause and get your sleep back.",
        "ggfqlLnQDly_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_ysadt1ysadt1ysad_1.png",
        "ggfqlLnQDly_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_ysadt1ysadt1ysad_1.png",
        "ggg77v9hBwa_label": "<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Apply My Discount</span></p>",
        "gggnu-lAaJZ_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:18px;\">By Dr. Mike Reynolds, MD, Urologist | 22 Years in Practice</span></p>",
        "ggh160fHHML_text": "<p>My inbox has been flooded with the same question.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>\"Do pumpkin seed oil and saw palmetto actually work for BPH, or is this just another supplement that does nothing?\"</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I've been a practicing urologist for 22 years.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I've prescribed every drug available for prostate problems.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Flomax. Finasteride. Avodart. Cialis for BPH. All of it.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>When this pack started getting attention in patient forums, I was skeptical.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The claims seemed impossible:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>- Reduces nighttime bathroom trips without a prescription</p><p>- Targets the actual root cause of prostate swelling</p><p>- No dependency, no withdrawal</p><p>- Men sleeping through the night within weeks</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But hundreds of men, including some of my own patients, were asking about it.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>So I investigated.</p>",
        "ggh9cc1rGQp_text": "<ul><li>Men waking up 3 or more times a night</li><li>Men who feel Flomax is working less and less</li><li>Men who can't stand the side effects of their current medication</li><li>Men who have been told surgery might be the next step</li><li>Men who tried generic saw palmetto and felt nothing</li><li>Men who want to fix the root cause, not rent relief month to month</li></ul>",
        "ggm20EezU0k_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_jh7z5ujh7z5ujh7z_1.png",
        "ggm20EezU0k_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_jh7z5ujh7z5ujh7z_1.png",
        "ggslWqaQtq2_text": "<strong>The 90-Day Investigation</strong>",
        "ggwChdnTNBJ_text": "<strong>The Problems With Flomax Nobody Discusses</strong>",
        "ggzQNDTTgV1_text": "<strong>I Spent 90 Days Investigating </strong><span style=\"background-color:rgba(249, 195, 47, 0.77);\"><strong>MeridEase Labs' Pumpkin Seed Oil and Saw Palmetto Softgels</strong></span><strong> to See If They Actually Work. Here's What I Found.</strong>",
